{
  "stem": "304.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they did two, two jobs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They saved our lives and including their own, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they had a lot of guts to fight the SS.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the bombing, what happened-- nobody bombed Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We know it today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "After the war, I found out that this was the night when inmates, who succeeded after months of collecting, piece by piece, explosives, they exploded two, two crematorias.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They succeeded.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There was a little rebellion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And two of the crematorias exploded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And some SS were killed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I left Auschwitz, so I don't know what happened later.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But after the war, I found out this, this is what the sirens were for.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And this is what happened at that night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I, I heard it after the war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know the date.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the 4th of October, supposedly, yeah.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what I had the feeling about going away from Auschwitz, it was true.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the other camp, we worked very hard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the food was better.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had our single-bed bunk beds, only two layers, not three levels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And everything was different.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But we had to work very hard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there, I was also very lucky in a certain way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[DRINKS] I, I didn't-- we had to-- we made a Panzerfaust, was a, a anti-tank missile, a small one.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Two girls worked at a machine.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And then we started-- made, like-- for one machine, I was working in the welding department.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One girl put up the, the, the pipe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the, the other had to hold it-- a little piece of plastic, had seven-- I don't remember how many holes.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we had to push 11 times the pedal-- the foot pedal to weld the little pipe-- the little metal piece on the pipe.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
